quote.summary: Jilin Jiutai Rural Commercial Bank Corp Ltd is a China-based company mainly engaged in banking business. The Company operates mainly through four segments. The Corporate Banking segment provides financial products and services to corporations and government agencies, including corporate loans and advances, deposit taking activities, agency services, consulting and advisory services, remittance and settlement services and guarantee services. The Retail Banking segment provides financial products and services to retail customers, including personal loans and deposit taking activities, bank card business, personal wealth management services and remittance services. The Treasury Operations segment covers the Group's treasury operations, including interbank money market transactions, repurchase transactions and investments, as well as the management of the Group's overall liquidity position, including the issuance of debts. The Others segment is engaged in other banking-related businesses.
